<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>:) } وَرْكنُ،<span class="c5"> كجَعْفَرٍ:</span> قَرْيةٌ ببُخَارى.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c5">! ووركانُ:</span> محلَّةٌ بأَصْفهانَ.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
